{"tid":1862126,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【教大】召喚所有教大宿生","createTime":"2020-02-04T12:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T16:52:06.000Z","uid":347318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e177a2902ade7544fdc228b7232118aec2491dcb","tid":1862126,"uid":347318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"啱啱學校出咗email叫宿生揀一係：<br />\n1. 提早退宿＋退宿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（2月12號或之前搬走、退咗宿嘅宿生之後冇得住返）<br />\n2. 繼續住，但佢會調你房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬呀 咪咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會退宿嘅都係本地學生 因為佢地有得返屋企住<br />\n想將宿舍俾NDS做隔離都唔係咁樣逼走啲local呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要未講幾時復課嘅情況之下要啲宿生咁急做決定？<br />\n萬一三月真係復課 要返返大埔上堂 但又冇宿舍住咁點呀？<br />\n都係因為住得遠先住hall姐 唔通貪你個hall多昆蟲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CLS<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aiKOPD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaiKOPD7.png&h=01b472df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vgEOPD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvgEOPD8.png&h=c83c2971&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"819b3b5623cb8be4f57bca574765186535b1c1fa","tid":1862126,"uid":140813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n現在如何？"},{"pid":"e42a1ec6d0240ff8a5c77649fb7b71d1fba2b08e","tid":1862126,"uid":347318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"819b3b5623cb8be4f57bca574765186535b1c1fa","tid":1862126,"uid":140813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n現在如何？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"星期三學生會、宿生會同學校開咗會<br />\n依家話：<br />\n1. 決定退唔退宿嘅deadline推遲到另行通知<br />\n2. 退宿期去到28/2<br />\n3. 將會成立學生代表小組，話會制定政策前諮詢學生<br />\n4. 真係復課而宿舍又開放嘅話，會俾揀退宿嘅同學優先重新申請宿位<br />\n5. 學校如果發現有同學虛報健康申報表，會<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮</span>轉交學生紀律委員會處理<br />\n6. 校方係公佈新隔離安排前，<span style=\"color: red;\">暫</span>不使用學生宿舍做隔離<br />\n<br />\n其實學校冇清楚交代點樣處置NDS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係另外send咗email<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">強烈建議</span></span>佢地留係大陸，假如佢地真係返咗黎都冇任何隔離措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望快啲有關於學費同復課嘅消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbetween, 學生會做野又幾快嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}